casebody.data:
BAUERLIEN v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 84,

September Term, 1965.]

Decided January 6, 1966. Before Prescott, C. J., and Hammond, Marbury, OppEnhEimer and McWieliams, JJ. Per Curiam.

For the reasons given by Judge Evans in his opinion below, the application for leave to appeal will be denied.

Application denied.
